<tr>=20
<td style=3D"font-family:'Open Sans',Arial,sans-serif;"> <h2 style=3D"font-=
weight:400; font-size:24px; line-height:30px; padding:0; margin:0 0 15px 0;=
">4. New models and methods are emerging.</h2> <p style=3D"padding:0; margi=
n:0 0 15px 0;"> While deep learning continues to drive a lot of interesting=
 research, most end-to-end solutions are hybrid systems. In 2020 we=E2=80=
=99ll hear more about the essential role of other components and methods=E2=
=80=94including Bayesian and other model-based methods, tree search, evolut=
ion, knowledge graphs, simulation platforms, and others. We also expect to =
see new use cases for reinforcement learning emerge. And we just might begi=
n to see exciting developments in machine learning methods that <em>aren=E2=
=80=99t</em> based on neural networks. </p> </td>=20
</tr>=20
